abstract: Andrew Delbanco reviews book Where You Go Is Not Who You'll Be: An Antidote to the College Admissions Mania by Frank Bruni.
lead_paragraph: This book reminds young people, and their parents, that what students get from a college has almost nothing to do with where it stands in the pecking order of prestige.

headline.main: Review: In ‘Where You Go Is Not Who You’ll Be,’ Frank Bruni Examines College Admissions Mania
headline.print_headline: Amid the Mania, Keeping the Allure of Elite Colleges in Perspective
